title: Estrada leads Blue Jays over Royals 7-1 to force ALCS Game 6
text: > Top News Estrada leads Blue Jays over Royals 7-1 to force ALCS Game 6 Toronto Blue Jays' Kevin Pillar, right, is tagged out by Kansas City Royals third baseman Mike Moustakas as he slides into third base on an attempted triple during the eighth inning in Game 5 of baseball's American League Championship Series on Wednesday, Oct. 21, 2015, in Toronto. Third base umpire Laz Diaz looks on. (Frank Gunn/The Canadian Press via AP) MANDATORY CREDIT
